src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618851B00000578-5057247-image-a-1_1510044314561.jpg&h=6ca15569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/4618868700000578-5057247-image-a-18_1510044513375.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618868700000578-5057247-image-a-18_1510044513375.jpg&h=d87e78a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/4618864F00000578-5057247-image-a-9_1510044383433.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618864F00000578-5057247-image-a-9_1510044383433.jpg&h=f84e73c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOne festive Uber driver made the effort to make his car look the part while giving out candy canes to passengers<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/4618866300000578-5057247-image-a-14_1510044447557.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618866300000578-5057247-image-a-14_1510044447557.jpg&h=ada47b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n This passenger was thrilled with the in-car entertainment in the form of a Nintendo game <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/4618866700000578-5057247-image-a-16_1510044491734.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618866700000578-5057247-image-a-16_1510044491734.jpg&h=5c7d61dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n There was no danger of this passenger's phone running out of juice thanks to this cabby <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/4618867700000578-5057247-image-a-17_1510044495323.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618867700000578-5057247-image-a-17_1510044495323.jpg&h=6be8d24f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n In the hope of securing some more five star ratings this driver provided a myriad of essentials for his customers <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/4618850D00000578-5057247-image-a-2_1510044318711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618850D00000578-5057247-image-a-2_1510044318711.jpg&h=3dab92c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n One Uber employee had gone to extreme lengths to fit a TV into the head-rest of the car<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/4618857700000578-5057247-image-a-3_1510044325794.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618857700000578-5057247-image-a-3_1510044325794.jpg&h=e38e719a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n A dog-loving passenger was thrilled at the prospect of a four-legged friend joining them for their journey <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/4618865300000578-5057247-image-a-10_1510044390636.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618865300000578-5057247-image-a-10_1510044390636.jpg&h=3847145a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Clearly in the Christmas spirit this driver provided each of his passengers with a holiday card<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/461886AF00000578-5057247-image-a-20_1510044541525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F461886AF00000578-5057247-image-a-20_1510044541525.jpg&h=d64376ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n There was no chance of this passenger going hungry as he tucked into one of the many snacks on board <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/461886B300000578-5057247-image-a-21_1510044553507.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F461886B300000578-5057247-image-a-21_1510044553507.jpg&h=9b256464&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Snacks, hand sanitizer and even moisturiser have been provided by this well-prepared driver<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/4618865B00000578-5057247-image-a-19_1510044524191.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618865B00000578-5057247-image-a-19_1510044524191.jpg&h=7830f0d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n When his radio stopped working this driver made every effort to entertain his customer - who was less than impressed<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/4618865F00000578-5057247-image-a-12_1510044421154.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618865F00000578-5057247-image-a-12_1510044421154.jpg&h=aaed45af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n James was sure to make his passengers as comfortable as possible with the many amenities on board <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/461886BD00000578-5057247-image-a-23_1510044586370.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F461886BD00000578-5057247-image-a-23_1510044586370.jpg&h=5e80ccd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n There are sweets aplenty in this generous Uber driver's car, much to the delight of his customers<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/4618855700000578-5057247-image-a-11_1510044405254.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618855700000578-5057247-image-a-11_1510044405254.jpg&h=53f79ae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Seth was eager to warn his customers that he wasn't ignoring them, but pointed out that they could play music as loud as they please<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/4618858B00000578-5057247-image-a-4_1510044333519.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618858B00000578-5057247-image-a-4_1510044333519.jpg&h=7b131dc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nThe Toyota Prius might be the car of choice for many Uber drivers, but this passenger was in for a more luxurious ride <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/461886C100000578-5057247-image-a-25_1510044602609.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F461886C100000578-5057247-image-a-25_1510044602609.jpg&h=9c2edbdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOne customer was a little surprised to discover that he would be joined by a four-legged passenger <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/4618864500000578-5057247-image-a-5_1510044339280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618864500000578-5057247-image-a-5_1510044339280.jpg&h=1300a6d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/4618867F00000578-5057247-image-a-22_1510044564556.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618867F00000578-5057247-image-a-22_1510044564556.jpg&h=eb12a08e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/4618853400000578-5057247-image-a-7_1510044352111.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618853400000578-5057247-image-a-7_1510044352111.jpg&h=0a8b4146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/07/08/4618856C00000578-5057247-image-a-8_1510044368182.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F08%2F4618856C00000578-5057247-image-a-8_1510044368182.jpg&h=d4353dcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58178a48313dac53bd3da9c7062617aa354337fd","tid":463481,"uid":10775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:31:11.000Z","msg":"雖然無搭過 但最少話比我地知有司機在乎客人 <br />\n<br />\n希望班賤畜唔好見到篇文一關的士事就亂咁吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7de2121a0a46082aeade05dd2dc0517a777abf","tid":463481,"uid":108831,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:33:05.000Z","msg":"淨係會諗點解人地會簡搭uber而唔搭的士呢點 對於一個年過50既中年人黎講真係好難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班dc9係到嘈人地搭uber唔搭的士 又唔諗點解消費者寧比貴啲都要搭uber"},{"pid":"dba6dc6479bcd5429f1c2594afa01df4467df507","tid":463481,"uid":108831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:33:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係會諗點解人地會簡搭uber而唔搭的士呢點 對於一個年過50既中年人黎講真係好難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班dc9係到嘈人地搭uber唔搭的士 又唔諗點解消費者<span style=\"color: red;\">寧願</span>比貴啲都要搭uber</blockquote>"}]}